data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home that features easy Maintenance Vinyl Siding, 30 Year Shingles, OPEN PLAN w/ Durable Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring in Great Room that is Open to Kitchen w/ Island, Beautiful Cabinetry, Granite Countertops, Pantry, & Stainless Steel Appliances. SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN w/ Private Master Bedroom w/ Tray Ceiling & Double Walk In Closets. Master Bath offers Separate Garden Tub & Shower, & Dual Vanity w/ Marble Countertops. Spacious Guest BDs w/Nice Closets & Hall Bath Features a Dual Vanity. Beautiful Tile Floors in Baths & Laundry Room. Relax on the Covered Back Porch with extension overlooking a nice fenced in Backyard. It also has a Sod & Sprinkler System and a 2- Car Garage.  THIS HOME COMES WITH MANY UPGRADES LIKE GUTTERS, A SHED, BEAUTIFUL STAINLESS STEEL REFRIGERATOR, FENCE AND ALSO AN EXTENDED PATIO THAT DID NOT COME WITH THE HOME WHEN IT WAS PURCHASED FROM BUILDER. This beautiful Home won't last long.  Owners need to sell for Job relocation.
